AD_VAL_RULE.NAME: ssrfc_budgetline_validation
AD_VAL_RULE.CODE: sfb_budget_line_id in (select sfb_budget_line_id from sfb_budget_line bl inner join sfb_budget_version bv on bl.sfb_budget_version_id = bv.sfb_budget_version_id inner join sfb_budget b on b.sfb_budget_id = bv.sfb_budget_id where budget_status = 'AP' and b.type_of_budget = 'SSRFC_BC' and bl.Actual_Value > 0)
